    "description": "<br><br>Sail on your own, fish, explore islands, and live the ultimate yachting lifestyle. Whether you're a seasoned sailor or new to the open waters, the freedom of yacht life is yours to enjoy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Open Waters</h2>The ocean is your playground. Navigate through stunning waterscapes, discovering hidden gems and exotic islands. This isn’t just a game; it’s your maritime adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/3ef6908a9f7d4cdacb5179c5950c9612.poster.avif?t=1729021256\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/3ef6908a9f7d4cdacb5179c5950c9612.webm?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/3ef6908a9f7d4cdacb5179c5950c9612.mp4?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Ideal Spots</h2>Your yachting choices are as vast as the sea itself. Choose your ideal spots from a variety of locations, each offering unique experiences and challenges. Prefer a serene lagoon or an adventurous island? The choice is yours, and it influences your game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/b047fe211c5e40dca0d8df69add2ec2f.poster.avif?t=1729021256\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/b047fe211c5e40dca0d8df69add2ec2f.webm?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/b047fe211c5e40dca0d8df69add2ec2f.mp4?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Your Yacht</h2>Select from a range of yachts, from modern designs to luxurious classics, each with distinct features. Customize your yacht with upgrades, sell it for profit, or turn it into a masterpiece of your own design. Your decision!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/24a189a16c5bd58ad5137503120cf41d.poster.avif?t=1729021256\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/24a189a16c5bd58ad5137503120cf41d.webm?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/24a189a16c5bd58ad5137503120cf41d.mp4?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Weather</h2>Weather plays a crucial role in your adventure. A sunny day might be perfect for a fishing trip, while a stormy night adds a thrilling challenge to your voyage. Adapt your strategy and embrace the dynamic weather patterns for an immersive experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/bc8f62a2f81f88734ee24dc9f553cdfd.poster.avif?t=1729021256\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/bc8f62a2f81f88734ee24dc9f553cdfd.webm?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/bc8f62a2f81f88734ee24dc9f553cdfd.mp4?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engage with Customers</h2>Interact with customers through your in-game social media page. Like their photos, post your own, and engage with comments. Schedule island tours, meet new clients, and earn money to expand your yachting empire.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/3cdfdd2b589fc72dd8b3ae3cf9f0921c.poster.avif?t=1729021256\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/3cdfdd2b589fc72dd8b3ae3cf9f0921c.webm?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/3cdfdd2b589fc72dd8b3ae3cf9f0921c.mp4?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand and Upgrade</h2>Invest in food and drinks for your trips, fish and sell your catch, upgrade your yacht’s interiors, rent boats, or hire crew members for automated tours.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/60fc816ff90e6d8ae369f16a3f7bfcce.poster.avif?t=1729021256\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/60fc816ff90e6d8ae369f16a3f7bfcce.webm?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124870/extras/60fc816ff90e6d8ae369f16a3f7bfcce.mp4?t=1729021256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>The freedom of the sea is yours. There's much more to discover. Are you ready to set sail and create your own adventure?",
